{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The Guise Empire,\u00a0without its original benefactor at the helm, is left running what hidden networks and monopolies it had across the Solar System. Having defeated their archenemy, the heroes begin to restore order to Avium, but Jake and Sarah must deal the loss of Derek. Haz-Mat's empty shell, GAMMA's propriety data, and quantum components were all brought to the scientist Nico for the sole purpose of <strong>reviving the world-renowned</strong> <strong>Droid</strong>.\u00a0Without  the expertise from a digital edge-lord like him, it'll be impossible to win the hearts of Aviuns and continue steering Avium into an age of peace, putting an end to the power vacuum and totalitarian reign many had sought..</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Play as both Sarah and Jake in this <strong>DLC</strong>:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Jake, as Diezel, departs from Earth to join up with GAMMA on the newly terraformed Mars in the wake of the Guise collapse. However, a miscalculated systems error forces him to make a crash-landing, which separates him from his Prometheus suit and his A.I., Synthia. Take turns playing as Synthia and Jake until the two are reunited.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2805380/extras/FInal_Gif1.gif?t=1739824642\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Sarah, as Valkyrie, takes on the quest of obtaining the final piece they need for Derek's revival: Derek's virtual mind or in other words his entire online presence in the form of his Cryo Pilot profile. Navigate the Entertainment District and infiltrate Techknight Territory to steal back the tablet guarded deep within their lair.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2805380/extras/FInalGif2.gif?t=1739824642\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p>","background":"https://store.akamai.steamstatic.com